<p>This isn’t a one-trick pony. The sporty design works with jeans and a t-shirt just as well as with business casual. At $152.94, you’re getting an in-house automatic movement for less than what many microbrands charge for generic movements.</p>

<h2>The Bottom Line</h2>
<p>Orient continues to prove that affordable mechanical watches don’t have to cut corners.</p>
